des:
Improve your sexual health with Kegel Crunches, an exercise program guaranteed to improve your performance and pleasure in the sack!

How to use this Skill:
Say, "Alexa, open Kegel Crunches" and begin your workout. 
Say, "Start" to begin the workout, then pick your gender. 
Say, "Help", if you want to learn about what to do in the skill.
Say, "Learn More", to learn about all of the benefits of Kegel muscle exercise. Not only are there sexual benefits, but general health as well!
